l;\">但相對的劣勢也不少，其中最令人詬病的便是製造及維修成本。由於引擎的本體為左右各一的配置，因此無論汽缸本體、上座、凸輪軸等都要雙倍，不僅耗時費工，成本也提升許多，再加上引擎室內除了引擎本體外並非對稱式的結構，因此引擎腳與周邊配件的安裝鎖點也不盡相同，組成零件也不一樣，所以在維修上也更為不便。另外由於水平對臥引擎本體呈現扁平狀，因此在冷卻系統、機油潤滑等方面都需要特別設計，效果也不如一般的直式引擎出色<span style=\"color: gold;\"></span></span>。"},{"pid":"7e8bd4fbdf2508a9612f1f48393814903e095a04","tid":788959,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:06:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 學到野"},{"pid":"6eae85f91aa8dd31f433ce12a556d667461f6603","tid":788959,"uid":32013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d7d3815be574c59a199b026ca0782981fec8ab8","tid":788959,"uid":75653,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T02:48:23.000Z","msg":"水平好似難散熱 所以頂盡直4冇直6"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T13:43:19.000Z","msg":"水平同直四/直四有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df71df484381d9ea506e25497c8c3d9e8a972c48","tid":788959,"uid":32013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad89c43aa0178fbd33ea9e021120cbd3e79cc717","tid":788959,"uid":169435,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"8d7d3815be574c59a199b026ca0782981fec8ab8","tid":788959,"uid":75653,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T02:48:23.000Z","msg":"水平好似難散熱 所以頂盡直4冇直6"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T02:52:04.000Z","msg":"你當波子，同法拉利死？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T13:45:19.000Z","msg":"法拉利果個只係廣義上的水平對向<br />\n狹義上只係180&deg;夾角V12☺"},{"pid":"15d90d4f3a4155aa39b924527a0a98c277d04383","tid":788959,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T13:46:15.000Z","msg":"咩係轉子引擎"},{"pid":"4e3834bf030d4dd1c51a2273d1f02d4146bf80cb","tid":788959,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15d90d4f3a4155aa39b924527a0a98c277d04383","tid":788959,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T13:46:15.000Z","msg":"咩係轉子引擎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":